title: 820-00164-A Green light, fan spin, no boot.
message:
Hi, hot an 820-00164-A board with no visible damage, green light and fan comes on, but no image, chime or boot. Doesn't boot on SMC bypass mode. 

Replaced BIOS chip, no change

PPVCC_S0_CPU: 1.8v

ALL_SYS_PWRGD: 3.3v

SMC_RESET_L: 3.4v

title: 820-00164-A Green light, fan spin, no boot.
message:
Do you get PLT_RESET_L?
Did you test the board alone on the desk?
How the fault appeared?

title: 820-00164-A Green light, fan spin, no boot.
message:
PLT_RESET_L is 3.3v 

User says he was just using it and it shut down.

title: 820-00164-A Green light, fan spin, no boot.
message:

Check all voltages from page 11.

title: 820-00164-A Green light, fan spin, no boot.
message:

title: 820-00164-A Green light, fan spin, no boot.
message:
"USB ports have power"
I didn't ask that.
You have sufficient time in the forum, to know how to check for USB ACTIVITY (not power).

title: 820-00164-A Green light, fan spin, no boot.
message:

title: 820-00164-A Green light, fan spin, no boot.
message:
